# Site origin only, or full https://host/buildathon/vote (path is stripped).
# In the shell: export VOTE_SMOKE_BASE_URL=https://example.com — no space after =.
# For multi-run or load testing, use staging or localhost—do not point a loop/cron at production.
#
# Examples:
# VOTE_SMOKE_BASE_URL=https://your-staging.example.com
# VOTE_SMOKE_BASE_URL=https://buildathon.cursorsrilanka.com
#
VOTE_SMOKE_BASE_URL=
